Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.83,0:00:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天會有什麼好事發生呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.26,0:00:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晨，小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.59,0:00:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晨，毘毘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.13,0:01:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡水的溫度可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.26,0:01:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛好啊，毘毘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.54,0:01:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天又是如此皎潔的月光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.34,0:01:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是它將不幸壟罩了這個星球嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.28,0:01:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是煩惱者之靈魂的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.62,0:01:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.62,0:01:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.49,0:01:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到正在痛苦掙扎的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.29,0:01:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈魂的叫聲…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.63,0:01:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又聽到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.96,0:01:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.63,0:01:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再讓我們的故鄉被疏遠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.30,0:01:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一起去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.65,0:01:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.00,0:02:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有煩惱的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.27,0:02:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請來愛情占星的香虹夜館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.82,0:02:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等，妳幹什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.75,0:02:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.39,0:02:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.36,0:02:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該進去了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.03,0:02:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.03,0:02:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.37,0:02:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過有多少人就有多少煩惱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.04,0:02:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毘毘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.38,0:03:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離和美見面時間還有一個小時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.19,0:03:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到現在都還不敢牽手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.52,0:03:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美香一定又會生氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.79,0:03:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…這樣不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.79,0:03:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，今天要和美香做…做…做…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.13,0:03:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行，我沒勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.54,0:03:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種面紙快點扔掉它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.07,0:03:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有怨言嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.44,0:03:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.11,0:03:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.45,0:03:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面紙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.78,0:03:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.92,0:03:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛情占星的香虹夜館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.13,0:03:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真悠閒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.47,0:03:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.80,0:03:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.14,0:03:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有客人來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.25,0:04:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎，請到這裡來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.17,0:04:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.83,0:04:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什…沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.24,0:04:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有愛情上的煩惱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.84,0:04:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.51,0:04:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，開始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.26,0:04:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是山羊座的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.20,0:04:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.47,0:04:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表看起來好像很穩重而內向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.87,0:05:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實內在隱藏著強烈的攻擊性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.34,0:05:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了達成目的相當謹慎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.28,0:05:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後雖然可以達成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.08,0:05:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是畏懼不前而導致災害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.48,0:05:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而要承擔這個疏忽卻很困難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.55,0:05:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很孤僻的性格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.36,0:05:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何？我說對了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.56,0:05:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說…說對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.70,0:05:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女朋友是天蠍座的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.24,0:05:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.17,0:05:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於事物的兩面性相當在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.51,0:05:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在她心靈世界裡充滿了神秘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.91,0:05:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個能源不是往外而是向內的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.18,0:05:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太愛說話，只會表達意見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.72,0:05:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以有時候會引起誤會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.79,0:05:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時擁有謙虛及尊嚴的她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.93,0:05:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很辣手的對象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.93,0:06:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是沒有勇氣坦率地示愛呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.27,0:06:11.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.94,0:06:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.41,0:06:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從剛剛令你坐立不安的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.61,0:06:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個原因啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.95,0:06:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.62,0:06:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只稍微碰一下女孩子的身體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.02,0:06:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心臟就會噗噗地跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.29,0:06:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像要爆炸一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.29,0:06:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有二十分鐘就要和她見面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.16,0:06:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該怎麼辦呢？我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.63,0:06:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.10,0:06:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題就是改變你自己了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.11,0:06:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這…這不可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.41,0:06:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠離靈魂的黑暗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.32,0:06:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.99,0:06:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧，提起勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.32,0:06:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敗北及勝利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.19,0:07:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只差在一紙之隔的勇氣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.64,0:07:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.84,0:07:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜，還差那麼一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.45,0:07:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐，他停止心跳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.59,0:07:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是刺激得太強烈了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.32,0:07:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.79,0:07:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看，還活著的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.00,0:07:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.00,0:07:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毘毘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.00,0:07:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.80,0:07:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撇開剛剛的話題不說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.27,0:07:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他應該和女朋友有約會的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.74,0:07:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這件事情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.94,0:07:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記住不要遲到了，送他去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.68,0:07:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.75,0:08:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半途而廢真掃興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.62,0:08:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和女朋友的約會就要遲到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.36,0:08:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.76,0:08:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒有辦法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.03,0:08:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾開！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.04,0:08:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人嘔心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.32,0:08:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個不知感恩圖報的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.72,0:08:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.79,0:08:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下，美香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.33,0:08:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？美香，等我一下啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.80,0:08:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了？美香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.14,0:08:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聰，我最討厭你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.14,0:08:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底什麼事呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.08,0:08:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.48,0:09:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只帶我去天文台和電動玩具店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.41,0:09:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時候也去別的地方不行嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.88,0:09:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…星星很漂亮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.69,0:09:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩電玩又可以令人很興奮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.42,0:09:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，你就自己一個人享受吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.89,0:09:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已經交往了3個月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.16,0:09:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事都沒發生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.49,0:09:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是不正常？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.10,0:09:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你可以正眼看看我這張臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.03,0:09:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這充滿朝氣的身體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.17,0:09:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣，不是問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.77,0:09:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.57,0:09:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指去酒店的事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.44,0:09:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢材！算了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.05,0:09:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短視，膽小鬼，陰險小人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.32,0:09:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,髒鬼，沒有用的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.45,0:09:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聰，我們還是不要再見面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.66,0:09:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…這是什麼意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.80,0:09:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說分手…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.20,0:10:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了，聰，再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.90,0:10:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不值得同情的小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.17,0:10:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.30,0:10:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才那麼一點點的創傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.17,0:10:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.51,0:10:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摸索出壟罩著小姐更加深遠的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.78,0:10:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈魂的叫聲所帶來的波動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.38,0:10:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才是首先要解決的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.85,0:10:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊，但是變得越來越有趣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.33,0:11:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回來了，這麼早啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.20,0:11:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聰，你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.80,0:11:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天花了些錢買了上等牛肉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.94,0:11:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上就吃小火鍋吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.21,0:11:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.14,0:11:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不吃？是小火鍋，小火鍋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.41,0:11:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聰，又只剩我一個人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.02,0:11:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時候也一起吃飯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.23,0:11:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…可惡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.43,0:11:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…可惡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.18,0:11:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.59,0:12:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聰，我進來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.59,0:12:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？聰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.27,0:12:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聰，聰！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.60,0:12:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作點，聰！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.61,0:12:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聰！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.99,0:12:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.29,0:12:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.02,0:12:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐，怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.23,0:12:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是那個呼喚著我的歌聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.36,0:12:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去追救護車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.63,0:12:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.50,0:12:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是從那個房間傳出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.66,0:13:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是電視遊樂器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.27,0:13:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從裡面傳來很強烈的信念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.80,0:13:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來不是人類的叫聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.81,0:13:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠離靈魂的黑暗面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.08,0:13:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有反應了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.68,0:13:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫做香虹夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.45,0:13:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在尋找有煩惱者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.42,0:13:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是隨從叫毘毘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.05,0:13:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要求援助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.29,0:13:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來，把心靈打開，給予愛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.27,0:13:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在電視遊樂器裡面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.40,0:13:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是這裡將人的心關在裡面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.61,0:13:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時候突然集中意念的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.74,0:14:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈魂變成有形物體的情形也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.75,0:14:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的情形來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.88,0:14:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了排除失戀的傷痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.62,0:14:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而迷上了電視遊樂器吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.62,0:14:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果將這個遊戲結束的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.56,0:14:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈魂也可以得到解放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.10,0:14:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來個冒險之旅吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.84,0:14:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.10,0:14:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.07,0:14:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.21,0:14:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼東西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.14,0:14:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼不早點說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.41,0:14:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.48,0:14:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，什麼東西啊，令人作嘔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.82,0:14:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等…等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.49,0:14:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要，不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.09,0:14:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在那邊發呆了，幫幫忙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.83,0:14:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，是，知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.09,0:14:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法槌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.17,0:14:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一把東方寶劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.44,0:15:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快一點啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.54,0:15:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在做了，再等一會兒就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.44,0:15:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.38,0:15:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會有這麼大的轉變？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.45,0:15:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.12,0:15:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了拯救小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.73,0:15:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好使出遊戲中的舞步了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.46,0:15:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.13,0:15:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.41,0:15:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連我都有這個遭遇嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.18,0:15:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼身體…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.50,0:16:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體會到了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.50,0:16:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我再一次很狠地折磨你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.51,0:16:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.51,0:16:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.55,0:16:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不夠，不夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.55,0:16:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在才真正開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.57,0:16:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次又是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.57,0:16:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭，停手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.10,0:16:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼東西啊，不要過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.87,0:16:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.91,0:16:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭，討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.98,0:16:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是違反規則的啊，不要進來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.71,0:16:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，已經放進去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.78,0:16:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！不行！快走開啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.05,0:17:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來這真是不錯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.93,0:17:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕地大反攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.60,0:17:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毘毘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.60,0:17:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.34,0:17:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐，我來救妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.41,0:17:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡，看你做的好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.28,0:17:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的生氣了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.32,0:17:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聰!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.69,0:17:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是個好色之徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.02,0:17:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是被女孩子拋棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.69,0:17:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而變得骯髒怪異的聰的心靈吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.69,0:17:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我收聲，收聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.29,0:17:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你…看我怎麼對付你吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.30,0:17:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷惘的靈魂啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.50,0:17:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睜開眼睛好好看清楚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.30,0:17:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.97,0:17:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.30,0:17:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.42,0:18:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣遊戲就結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.62,0:18:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.62,0:18:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為可以再逞一下威風的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.69,0:18:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，還算不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.63,0:18:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.96,0:18:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，不小心打到小姐的頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.63,0:18:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是因為我急於完成任務啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.63,0:18:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.77,0:18:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼聲音呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.17,0:18:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定是遊戲的待續呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.64,0:18:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.31,0:18:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐，有光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.98,0:18:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…媽媽…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.98,0:18:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽！媽媽…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.65,0:18:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.06,0:18:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽！不要走…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.73,0:18:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此，從小就和母親分開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.33,0:18:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.60,0:18:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個家庭裡發生過什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.13,0:18:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，在他內心深處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.80,0:18:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於母親的記憶卻是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.14,0:18:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很深刻地殘留下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.40,0:18:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，遊戲輸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.67,0:18:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就逃到留有母親的回憶裡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.07,0:18:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.41,0:19:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的靈魂就會回到原來的地方吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.68,0:19:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.35,0:19:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等，小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.09,0:19:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的心靈成長在那時候就停止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.69,0:19:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以隱藏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.96,0:19:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他相當地需要母愛的一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.57,0:19:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像恢復正常了，毘毘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.70,0:19:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.17,0:19:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請在這裡小睡片刻吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.51,0:19:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠離靈魂的黑暗面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.65,0:19:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來，讓我聽聽你的煩惱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.52,0:19:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你希望媽媽留下來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.53,0:19:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聰，那些就是星座
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.27,0:19:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳聞是希臘女神的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.20,0:20:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強吮著女神的乳房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.07,0:20:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.40,0:20:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濺出來的奶水便點綴在天空中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.14,0:20:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而形成了星座啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.08,0:20:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.08,0:20:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主導他的命運之根就在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.55,0:20:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，我們回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.83,0:20:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好地吸吮它吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.43,0:20:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你一直
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.43,0:20:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來都吸吮著的乳房啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.30,0:20:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊吸吮著美味的乳汁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.64,0:20:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊成為堅強的男人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.24,0:20:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最後再吸吮一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.78,0:20:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你母親的乳房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.51,0:20:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可使你從母親的回憶中得到解放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.85,0:20:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來，再吸吮它吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.66,0:20:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，從乳房中畢業後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.86,0:20:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就會從男孩子而轉變成男人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.59,0:20:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很強，很強的男人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.73,0:21:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，對不會太過份了點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.94,0:21:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能令女孩子幸福的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.81,0:21:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不算是男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.01,0:21:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我成為強壯的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.15,0:21:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡到底是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.75,0:21:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是可以使你通往幸福的橋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.49,0:21:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.62,0:21:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我，不可以回頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.63,0:21:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不可以向後走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.63,0:21:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好地渡過這座橋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.17,0:21:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來，走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.52,0:21:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.65,0:21:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底怎麼了啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.86,0:22:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要那麼興奮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.39,0:22:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡面安靜地不要動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.53,0:22:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美香!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.21,0:22:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美香的乳房啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.61,0:22:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會有感覺啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.88,0:22:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.22,0:22:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.69,0:22:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在想什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.09,0:22:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這又是什麼感覺呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.89,0:22:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.56,0:22:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得到身體了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.30,0:22:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的，聰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.03,0:22:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美香是看不到我們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.64,0:22:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不管做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.37,0:22:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美香是不會知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.51,0:22:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到美香的身材這麼棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.91,0:22:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提起勇氣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.78,0:22:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣到真的要做的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.32,0:23:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心臟也不會因太緊張而導致休克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.92,0:23:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.32,0:23:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是…這樣好像是強暴似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.92,0:23:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又這樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.32,0:23:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你摸到她的身體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.33,0:23:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定就可以明白她的感受了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.93,0:23:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已是頂天立地的男人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.27,0:23:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要一直望向我，加油啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.27,0:23:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是看不到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.94,0:23:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好地做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.01,0:23:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，那我來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.68,0:23:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到聰的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.88,0:23:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體就突然地發熱起來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.95,0:23:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿聰…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.29,0:23:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.29,0:23:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.63,0:23:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聰…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.30,0:23:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你說那樣的話真是對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.77,0:23:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我是喜歡你的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.84,0:24:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想被阿聰你抱著啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.05,0:24:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算沒經驗的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.18,0:24:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以作到完美的技巧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.18,0:24:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是情報化的時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.66,0:24:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿聰…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.32,0:24:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高潮了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.99,0:24:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高潮了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.06,0:24:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿聰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.73,0:24:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣的!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.28,0:24:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的，阿聰正在醫院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:38.68,0:24:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會在那個地方睡著了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:41.55,0:24:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸還是不行啊，阿聰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:45.02,0:24:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是做不好母親這個角色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:53.36,0:24:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，阿聰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:56.70,0:24:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這回事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:58.50,0:25:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不需要母親了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:02.04,0:25:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:03.71,0:25:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就算不依賴對母親的回憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:06.58,0:25:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以好好地活下去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:08.38,0:25:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿聰，你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:10.71,0:25:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，看到你康復真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:13.38,0:25:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:15.05,0:25:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:18.12,0:25:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿聰，你醒了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:23.12,0:25:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:26.73,0:25:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:28.66,0:25:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿聰，上次真是很對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:32.54,0:25:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別介意，我沒事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:45.41,0:25:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:47.22,0:25:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我昨天經歷了一場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:48.92,0:25:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思議的體驗啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:50.49,0:25:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎麼樣的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:52.36,0:25:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像變強壯了啊，阿聰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:56.33,0:25:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事實上也是很強壯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:58.79,0:26:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼今天…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:00.10,0:26:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:02.20,0:26:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要去天文台嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:04.43,0:26:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去旅館啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:07.10,0:26:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:20.85,0:26:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充滿朝氣的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:22.79,0:26:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:23.79,0:26:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:28.19,0:26:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1999年7月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:31.59,0:26:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從恐怖的代表轉為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:33.13,0:26:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解救人類的愛的傳道師香虹夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:36.20,0:26:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出身，年齡不詳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:39.14,0:26:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
